suncertify.db
Class MetaData

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.db.MetaData
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataRow, java.io.Serializable
public final class MetaData
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataRow

This singleton is responsible for reading the meta data of the database file. Determines valid database files and throws appropriate exceptions.

Version:
1.1
Author:
Rohit Sood
